'''Taga Shrine''' (Taga Jinja) is an {{ill|UNKNOWN|lt=Engishiki shrine|1=UNKNOWN|WD=Q134917286|lt=Shikinaisha}} of {{ill|lt=Mutsu Province|Q907389|WD=Q907389}}, {{ill|lt=Miyagi District|Q1131751|WD=Q1131751}}, located in {{ill|UNKNOWN|lt=Rokugatsuzaka|1=UNKNOWN}}, {{ill|lt=Takasaki (Tagajō City)|UNKNOWN|lt=Takasaki}}, {{ill|lt=Tagajō City|Q653355|WD=Q653355}}, {{ill|lt=Miyagi Prefecture|Q47896|WD=Q47896}}. {{ill|lt=Ukishima Shrine (Tagajō City)|Q11558528|WD=Q11558528|lt=Ukishima Shrine}} is also one of the disputed shrines ({{ill|lt=ronsya|Q135022904|WD=Q135022904}}) for the {{ill|UNKNOWN|lt=Engishiki shrine|1=UNKNOWN|WD=Q134917286|lt=Shikinaisha}} “Taga Shrine” of {{ill|lt=Miyagi District|Q1131751|WD=Q1131751}}.

